Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}二人は平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向かない君は強い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}もう交わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs50}立ちつくす街は歪み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs50}君が居た記憶だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs50}胸の中に溢れ出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs50}深い海を創り　僕はそこに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:11.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs50}溺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:19.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必須前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}時間不會停留
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:33.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}心願被風吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:38.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}喉嚨乾澀沙啞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知前方有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你我就像一組平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}堅強的你從不回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們將永遠不再相交
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs60}我頹然而立 城市在視野中模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs60}只有你曾存在的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs60}衝垮心靈的堤壩
